{"tid":1005873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Citibank 個app好撚垃圾","createTime":"2019-02-02T13:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T15:43:59.000Z","uid":144848,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"08b5b6fa8bf039a63e11e4df20427e9478833f09","tid":1005873,"uid":144848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:53:09.000Z","msg":"之前係大學申請左張 Citibank信用卡<br />\n我就順便download Citibank 個app啦<br />\n註冊完成左之後<br />\n諗住入返密碼<br />\n係咁話我密碼錯誤<br />\n我再重設密碼，佢竟然話我戶口俾人封左<br />\n打去Call center<br />\n佢話線路繁忙等候3分鐘<br />\n我等左15分鐘先有人聽<br />\n我一開口就同佢講呢個app有問題，睇唔到張單<br />\n佢即刻呢就同我講，話囉我將你個電話轉去另外個部門<br />\n我總共等左30分鐘都冇人再聽我電話<br />\nCitibank 傻的嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c51f7acea86ee3e69762910e81d4bf7b577214c","tid":1005873,"uid":51932,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:56:01.000Z","msg":"今日先聽完個同事打過，兩下就有人聽喎<br />\n<br />\n佢打去免年費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec5f14526cba7c2710b5ecb7754c23c139dc42c","tid":1005873,"uid":132587,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:56:26.000Z","msg":"自己弱智唔記得密碼唔好賴app廢"},{"pid":"11fa77f436fd10fd51a255ac3129f41419aacc51","tid":1005873,"uid":126301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:04:04.000Z","msg":"試過好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5ce54684c38ca0d154f57651905e9edc9a3190","tid":1005873,"uid":35135,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:07:17.000Z","msg":"我個app login咗都睇唔到單，<br />\n轉唔到頁，<br />\n惟有用佢唔使login直接show account info個function<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之個app真係好廢"},{"pid":"dae5b63b8298e54d0f1db9398a2954be4ffbf55a","tid":